      "tombstone": "La Cervara, the Roman Campagna, c. 1830–31. Jean Baptiste Camille Corot (French, 1796-1875). Oil on fabric; framed: 130 x 167.5 x 9.5 cm (51 3/16 x 65 15/16 x 3 3/4 in.); unframed: 97.6 x 135.8 cm (38 7/16 x 53 7/16 in.). The Cleveland Museum of Art, Leonard C. Hanna, Jr. Fund 1963.91",
      "current_location": "219 19th Century European",
      "title": "La Cervara, the Roman Campagna",
      "title_in_original_language": null,
      "series": null,
      "series_in_original_language": null,
      "creation_date": "c. 1830–31",
