      "wall_description": "This rare silver cup is dated, inscribed, and impressed with a seal of the famous silversmith Zhu Bishan. Shaped like a hollow log, the cup can be filled through its upturned tip. The cup has an inscription on its back that alludes to a story of an immortal riding down a river. According to the story, the man lost his way and ended up in the Milky Way galaxy. He was temporarily transformed into a star, and met with the Weaving Maid, another star. The figure, in fact, holds a tablet labeled \"loom-supporting stone, \" a token of his encounter with the Weaving Maid.",
